{"tid":21311,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有鼻敏感嘅你 入一入嚟","createTime":"2016-12-03T18:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T08:14:10.000Z","uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c465505a8b75e9bdb86c66161ebc597717def4fe","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"由細到大都有鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉天氣 室外入有冷氣地方 就會打黑痴或流鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期鼻塞 有時講嘢唱歌會有鼻音<br />\n有無巴絲同我一樣<br />\n或者你地有無辦法可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d528f0474bebbff6a791db6fa5cb1aba0642066","tid":21311,"uid":16313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:26:08.000Z","msg":"天灸 幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677e624e467f6c898c8a840663cc6fa635d6b15b","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天灸 幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天灸即係針灸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51a9bcbcb87063bae5a3b38ff4e4768249e0e3c","tid":21311,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都有鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉天氣 室外入有冷氣地方 就會打黑痴或流鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期鼻塞 有時講嘢唱歌會有鼻音<br />\n有無巴絲同我一樣<br />\n或者你地有無辦法可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊住個日成日都做唔到野 鼻水係咁流"},{"pid":"f50e339bb63adaadc4f12ad30560bd9bab0b4abf","tid":21311,"uid":3923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:29:47.000Z","msg":"有個耳鼻喉醫生幾好，之前游左十幾年水(港隊咁濟)，中醫西醫都搞唔掂，佢控制到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話再唔得就切鼻甲"},{"pid":"67cc4156fdba3d76383bcfc97ad004ef19739218","tid":21311,"uid":36756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:32:10.000Z","msg":"做運動<br />\n提肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6390c4be1fe9544f4bfce14e89127e40823d1316","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都有鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉天氣 室外入有冷氣地方 就會打黑痴或流鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期鼻塞 有時講嘢唱歌會有鼻音<br />\n有無巴絲同我一樣<br />\n或者你地有無辦法可以好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊住個日成日都做唔到野 鼻水係咁流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最麻煩喺日日都要帶幾包紙巾 漸漸成為習慣"},{"pid":"860839cd4f8477563355275aa88f14a7d0ce2752","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個耳鼻喉醫生幾好，之前游左十幾年水(港隊咁濟)，中醫西醫都搞唔掂，佢控制到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話再唔得就切鼻甲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我細個都有睇耳鼻喉科 睇左幾年佢話我無事 點知咁就十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e97aa4181ec0ea3468a29ee8e8ab508292e521","tid":21311,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"留名睇方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一入商場連續瘋狂打十個黑痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離個阿姐係咪望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔想架"},{"pid":"244f75734b49328263c9595cb14e3b0a08529a71","tid":21311,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:34:52.000Z","msg":"之前睇私家睇撚左六千幾蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比左啲藥食同埋噴鼻 果排好好多<br />\n但一停左食藥同噴鼻又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574f99804b2cac621194e1d5b8cbc311ca1feccc","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做運動<br />\n提肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有做運動呀 本身我自己跑步嘅 最慘喺跑緊嗰陣會喺咁流"},{"pid":"631b22902387813a10a7c8b1d0e10532c93cba13","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一入商場連續瘋狂打十個黑痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離個阿姐係咪望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔想架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭車嗰陣 抺鼻涕 打黑痴會俾人歧視 坐我旁邊嗰啲食會即刻走開 有得坐都走開 心諗我無病嫁"},{"pid":"388cb766e24326824e6938be480ff2a0b4b0ea9b","tid":21311,"uid":36679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野有鼻音 成日比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed0e2950c2ac05b00dfd1e98fe61a0a4e2bf23d","tid":21311,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:39:03.000Z","msg":"我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多"},{"pid":"f8c48b3f9f2af26dae77d29be1c0da2188a546ff","tid":21311,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野有鼻音 成日比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依樣真<br />\n講野有鼻音，d人以為我嗲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：男"},{"pid":"99350e1b5eb4d047d20ccc9d91ea97d4d4ea548f","tid":21311,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:40:18.000Z","msg":"晚晚都想砍左個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1369853f8c1efcc5d5d90652fdbdde627e09ec","tid":21311,"uid":52743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪痴d bb屎咁既野係後面<br />\n<br />\n細個好似試過"},{"pid":"009ab1e83d75dec62ae7f19b923c07e69fa593a0","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前睇私家睇撚左六千幾蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比左啲藥食同埋噴鼻 果排好好多<br />\n但一停左食藥同噴鼻又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我細嗰睇耳鼻喉 嗰陣已經有噴鼻 無噴之後慢慢就無用"},{"pid":"da683b2baa808e6eca2882a82ca18d741e318f4b","tid":21311,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪痴d bb屎咁既野係後面<br />\n<br />\n細個好似試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔知用咩中藥加薑<br />\n有刺激性 貼1-3個鐘 睇皮膚<br />\n次次貼完好似曬傷咁"},{"pid":"51034e6fd14307cf9cfa0112ec5e8986a2a4c4e1","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野有鼻音 成日比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發音唔正咁款"},{"pid":"d8ad367af15dffd51144b5885f80fcd20f46e4d9","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪痴d bb屎咁既野係後面<br />\n<br />\n細個好似試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔知用咩中藥加薑<br />\n有刺激性 貼1-3個鐘 睇皮膚<br />\n次次貼完好似曬傷咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到有得做天灸"},{"pid":"85d911c0b70821eb2e44ec26b55428b8cc50b745","tid":21311,"uid":28727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:05:08.000Z","msg":"鼻塞先麻煩 要用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">口</span>呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f86bf176a85e3170beec70fcbe5f6b5724e28e8","tid":21311,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪痴d bb屎咁既野係後面<br />\n<br />\n細個好似試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔知用咩中藥加薑<br />\n有刺激性 貼1-3個鐘 睇皮膚<br />\n次次貼完好似曬傷咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到有得做天灸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年我無做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要塞到下年7月"},{"pid":"4a9fdb53f75de972c3f49f047efb0670f65f6afa","tid":21311,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:18:09.000Z","msg":"不過勤啲換床單勤啲清潔都有少少用👍🏿"},{"pid":"4132d699b5273bc249118659cbb1c68a60a3f215","tid":21311,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T19:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係做天灸<br />\n做左兩年已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪痴d bb屎咁既野係後面<br />\n<br />\n細個好似試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔知用咩中藥加薑<br />\n有刺激性 貼1-3個鐘 睇皮膚<br />\n次次貼完好似曬傷咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到有得做天灸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中醫果d都有<br />\n我之前係天水圍天恆東華三院唔知咩中醫度做<br />\n佢分夏天同冬天兩段時間做"}]}